Sets the position and rotation of the entity.
In contrast to [`teleportTo`](#teleportto), this method does not perform validity checks on coordinates.

**Parameters**
- `[js]x`, `[js]y`, `[js]z`: The new coordinates of the entity.
- `[js]yaw`, `[js]pitch`: The target rotation of the entity.

**Return value**
None (`[js]undefined`).

<<<

| <#setPositionAndRotation>             |
| <#setPositionAndRotation-description> |

