entity.absRotateTo(pitch, yaw)
```

Sets the entity's facing direction (yaw and pitch) while clamping the entity's yaw and pitch to valid values, that is - pitch must be within range `<0, 360)`, yaw must be within range `<​-90, 90>`.

**Parameters**
- `[js]pitch`, `[js]yaw`: The new pitch and yaw of the entity, in degrees.

**Return value**
None (`[js]undefined`).
<<<

| <#absRotateTo> |
| <#absRotateTo-description> |
