**Syntax**
```js
entity.copyPosition(otherEntity)
```

Copies the `[js]otherEntity`'s position, yaw and pitch onto the `[js]entity`.
In other words, it teleports `[js]entity` to `[js]otherEntity` and makes it look at the same direction as `[js]otherEntity`.

**Parameters**
- `[js]otherEntity`: Another {Entity}.

**Return value**
None (`[js]undefined`).
