<<<

>>> #isVisuallyCrawling-description

**Syntax**
```js
entity.isVisuallyCrawling()
entity.visuallyCrawling // read-only bean
```

Checks if the entity is visually crawling.

By default, entities are visually crawling if they are [visually swimming](#isvisuallyswimming), but they are **not** in water nor in any liquid the entity can swim in.

**Return value**
`[js]true` if the entity is visually crawling, `[js]false` if it isn't.
