```

Tries to mount the `[js]entity` on a `[js]vehicle`.

**Parameters**
- `[js]vehicle`: The {Entity} to start riding on.
- `[js]isForced` {optional}: Whether the mounting is forced. If `[js]false`, the entity will only be mounted if the `[js]entity` can ride vehicles and `[js]vehicle` has room for seating passengers. Defaults to `[js]false` if not provided.

**Return value**
`[js]true` if the `[js]entity` has been successfully mounted, `[js]false` if it hasn't.
